[21.790245, "o", "\u001b[1m\u001b[2m\u001b[7mExploring image generation\u001b(B\u001b[m                                                                                              \u001b[22;1H\u001b[2m\u001b[7mI'm considering how to generate images effectively. It seems like using Hugging Face space might be a good option, but I\u001b[23;1Hneed to explore and confirm that. I'm thinking about what tools and resources are available there for creating images, \u001b(B\u001b[m \u001b[24;1H\u001b[2m\u001b[7mas well as how to navigate those options efficiently. It's exciting to discover new methods, so I'll definitely look \u001b(B\u001b[m   \u001b[25;1H\u001b[2m\u001b[7minto that further!\u001b(B\u001b[m                                                                                                      \u001b[26;1H\r\n"]
